  <p>
    thewideangle.club exists because one topic was never going to be enough. We cover technology,
    travel, sport, credit cards, geopolitics, and experiences — six distinct beats under a single
    editorial voice.
  </p>
  <p>
    Every hero image and gallery you see here is original photography, shot and edited by the same
    person who writes the words. That is deliberate: the wide angle is both a literal lens and a
    point of view — pull back far enough, and technology, travel, money, and culture all turn out to
    be the same story.
  </p>
  <h2>How we work</h2>
  <p>
    We publish near-daily, batch content in sessions, and never run raw AI output — everything is
    human-edited for accuracy, originality, and voice before it goes live.
  </p>
  <h2>How we make money</h2>
  <p>
    This site is intentionally monetized from day one through a mix of display advertising, disclosed
    affiliate partnerships (particularly in credit cards and travel), and — as the audience grows —
    sponsorships and our own digital products. Full detail lives on our
    <a href="/disclosure/">affiliate disclosure</a> page.
  </p>
  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>
    Questions, pitches, partnership ideas, or a doubt about a credit card — WhatsApp, Instagram, email,
    or the form, whichever's easiest for you. <a href="/contact/">All the ways to reach us</a>.
